biotools.summary: RNA-seq pipeline for differential gene expression analysis (paired-end, pooled samples, animals). Illumina RNA Sequencing differential expression analysis pipeline between two collections of eukaryote samples. The collections represents the two conditions being compared, and the datasets in each collection is defined by the user.
